      "instruction": "<p>Once the potato is fork-tender, remove the pot from the heat<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>and add a splash of <strong>milk</strong></p><p>Blitz until smooth with a <strong>(stick) blender </strong>and<strong> </strong>season with a pinch<strong> </strong>of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> pepper </strong>–<strong> </strong>this is your<strong> mushroom soup</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of boiled water if the soup is looking a little thick!</p>",
